summary:
21st September, 2018.
Best day of my life. I was able to meet two of the people who are most important to me. They have...
body:
21st September, 2018.

Best day of my life. I was able to meet two of the people who are most important to me. They have literally saved my life on countless occasions. Whenever I would have had a really tough or bad day, Dan and Phil’s videos would be my safe haven. They literally gave me the courage to keep going. The mere idea that I might someday get to meet them would hold me together.

Now that it’s finally happened, I can barely wrap my head around it. To be able to see them, hug them and talk to them affected me in a way nothing ever has. They’re just such genuinely nice people you can’t help not falling in love with them. I still sort of feel like it was all a dream and that I’m going to wake up in the morning and realise that it has, in fact, not happened.

In any case, it did and it has given me enough good memories to look back upon on a bad day.

On a funnier note though I got to tell Dan that I hated him for bringing ‘The Ancient Magus’ Wife’ into my life just before I had to submit a super important report, thereby ruining my life and any hopes I had of being productive, and he just laughed and apologized. Phil and him then spoke about how everyone’s been in that situation before and omg my knees were shaking.

They then drew cat whiskers on my face.

Thank you so much for today @danielhowell and @amazingphil, you will never understand how much this meant to me and how important you are. Thank you for existing, see you on the internet somewhere!
